channel.itunes:summary: Alone? Depressed? Don't suffer in silence. Suffer listening to Suicide Radio! Suicide Radio plays dark and pounding beats. Your favorite goth, industrial, futurepop, EBM, and power noise music. Available as both mp3 and m4a podcasts. www.suicideradio.com
